&lt;p&gt;# Comments: 1&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48517988</guid><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 15:01:46 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Show HN: Chrome Extension That Removes AI Slop / Spam / Self-Promo from Reddit</title><link>https://nobot-two.vercel.app/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;I lately was really frustrated about all the ai content on reddit. I feel like every second post is just a bot trying to farm engagement. I dont want to invest my time "helping" or answering questions from a bot. Then came to my mind: "It would be so nice if there was something like sponsorblock that removes all the slop". I decided to play with chrome extensions and would like to share mine with you. It works by analyzing the posts OP and the content itself. I first check account age, post-to-comment ratio and profile picture. In the post content I check for links. Optional I also send the Post text to deepseek-v1-flash to check for intent of the post. It then gives me a score. I already got some feedback from my friends and now would like to improve it further. It is not perfect yet so I made it a closed beta. Also since it requires llm I have to be a bit cautious with access or else I am screwed XD.
Really interested in your thoughts.&lt;/p&gt;
